1.   Start the backend API: `npm run start --workspace=backend-api`
2.   Go to `frontend/utils/link.tsx`, uncomment Next.js link and comment out the custom implementation
3.   Go to `src/frontend/next-app-router/src/app` folder and add `use client` at the top of every `page` file inside to force everything to be Client Components. Remove all `use client` to revert back to reasonable amount of Server Components (without data fetching so far).
4.   Build the frontend: `npm run build --workspace=next-app-router`
5.   Start the frontend: `npm run start --workspace=next-app-router`
